items.title: 5.0 out of 5 stars Warm and soft
items.body: The sweater is excellent quality. The wool is soft and not itchy at all. The fit is flattering, and the color looks even better in person. Very satisfied — I’m already thinking of getting another one! Read more
items.author: Chuyan Wang

items.title: 5.0 out of 5 stars The perfect sweater
items.body: I recently tried the FINEAST V-Neck Women’s 100% Cashmere Undyed Natural Pullover Sweater, and it has a very classic, understated feel that makes it easy to wear in a variety of settings. The undyed cashmere gives it a soft, natural look, and the material itself feels lightweight yet warm. It has that gentle, cloud-soft texture you expect from real cashmere, and it’s comfortable enough to wear all day without feeling heavy or itchy. The fit is relaxed without being shapeless, and the V-neck is flattering while still modest enough for layering over camisoles or wearing alone. It pairs nicely with jeans, trousers, or skirts, and the simplicity of the design makes it one of those sweaters that can be dressed up or down without much effort. The knit has a smooth, even finish that lies nicely against the body, and the lack of dye gives it a very natural, minimal aesthetic that works well with neutral outfits. Because it’s pure cashmere, it does require gentle care, but that’s expected with this kind of material. Hand-washing or using a delicate wool cycle keeps it in good condition, and the sweater holds its shape well after drying. It’s warm enough for chilly days but breathable too, which makes it comfortable in indoor settings where heavier knits can feel too hot. Overall, the FINEAST cashmere pullover is soft, comfortable, and beautifully simple. Its undyed natural look gives it a timeless quality, and the lightweight cashmere makes it a cozy everyday piece that still feels refined. It’s a lovely choice if you want a sweater that feels luxurious without being flashy. Read more
items.author: Stephanie

items.title: 5.0 out of 5 stars Timeless, classic, luxurious!
items.body: FINEAST V-Neck Womens 100% Pure Cashmere Undyed Natural Pullover Sweater If you're looking for an extra-special gift that's practical but also luxurious, this soft, warm, neutral, 100% cashmere pullover sweater would be a great option. It's timeless and classic and will never go out of style. The natural undyed color makes a versatile canvas for a colorful scarf or statement necklace. I gifted this sweater to myself and I absolutely love it! Paired with plaid pull-on pants, high leather boots, a plaid scarf, pearls, and a trench coat it looked very classy. But it could be paired with almost anything, from jeans and sneakers to a skirt and heels or flats. The material is very soft. If you choose to give it as a gift to a special someone (other than yourself, like I did!), it comes beautifully boxed and carefully wrapped in tissue paper secured with a sticker and card. A hanging cedar(?) wood ball is included to help repel moths. This is an absolutely gorgeous sweater! Read more
items.author: Zen Yurt

items.title: 4.0 out of 5 stars FINEAST V-Neck Womens 100% Pure Cashmere Undyed Natural Pullover Sweater review
items.body: This is a lovely cashmere sweater. I gave it 4 stars due to the thinness of it because it is definitely see-through, as you can tell by my picture. I will wear another shirt under it, for sure. The large is okay on me, I am 5 ft, 145 lbs for reference. The sweater is not bulky, and will hug your curves. It is very soft, as cashmere should be. Overall, it's a very nice sweater that came in a nice presentation box. I don't know yet how well it will wear or clean. The color is white, but it is a shade of white more like eggshell, not a pure bright white. Read more
items.author: Steph's Reviews

items.title: 5.0 out of 5 stars Cozy, Elegant, and Timeless!
items.body: Excellent craftsmanship is displayed in the sweater, which is silky smooth, has a well-finished appearance, and elegantly maintains its shape after being washed. It is the timeless V-neck design that I adore. It is easy to pair with jeans, trousers, or skirts, and it is a flexible piece that flatters anybody. The natural hue is neutral and classic, which means that it can be worn with virtually anything. As a result, it is an essential component of my wardrobe. In spite of its little weight, it manages to keep me extremely warm even on days when the temperature is lower. Providing that you adhere to the care directions, the sweater is not only long-lasting but also requires little maintenance. I have been complimented on it on several occasions, and it has the genuine impression of being a luxury item. Read more
items.author: Elaine G

items.title: 5.0 out of 5 stars Exquisite sweater
items.body: I am so impressed with this sweater. The cashmere is a mid weight cashmere that is buttery soft and consistently spun and knit. It’s well constructed without overly bulky seams. It runs a bit small on US sizes, so order according to the fit you’d like. But the quality of this garment is really incredible. It is worth every penny. Truly this is exquisite. It also comes beautifully packaged with a cedar ball to prevent mothballs which would make this an incredible gift for a loved one! Read more
items.author: Ashley E

items.title: 5.0 out of 5 stars Classic
items.body: This is a classic style that will last years. It is presented and boxed beautifully, and will make a nice gift for Xmas. It also includes a cedar ball to keep moths away. It's cashmere, and cloud soft. The natural color goes with everything. If you want a special gift, this would qualify. If you are looking for winter basics, this would definitely fit the bill. I cannot address the fit, since it will be a gift; however, it looks like it is a comfortable fit without being snug. Everything about this sweater is classic. Read more
items.author: Eclectic reader

items.title: 5.0 out of 5 stars A beautiful and soft Cashmere sweater
items.body: This cashmere sweater arrived in an unbelievable giftbox. Unboxing was definitely quite an experience. This sweater is so light and ultra soft. The feel of the cashmere is also smooth and delicate. It is a very beautiful garment made with all-natural material! For a short woman like me the fit was right on. As a gift, it will make someone very happy. Read more
items.author: S R

short_description:
Womens Dress is made for a polished look that still feels comfortable to wear. It is designed to sit cleanly on the body with a flattering shape that works for day plans and dressier moments without feeling overdone.

The fit focuses on balance rather than extremes, so you can move naturally while still getting a defined silhouette. Choose your usual size for a closer look, or size up if you prefer a little more ease through the waist and hips.

Styling is simple: keep accessories minimal for a clean finish, or add a jacket and statement shoes when you want a sharper outfit. This piece photographs well thanks to smooth lines and a structured feel that stays put once you have it adjusted.

With the right fit and simple styling, this item becomes an easy go-to when you want something that looks intentional without requiring extra effort.

This piece transitions well from daytime plans to evening events with a quick change of shoes and a small bag or clutch.

To keep it looking sharp, follow the care label first and avoid high heat when drying or steaming if the material is sensitive.

long_description:
Womens Dress is a versatile piece you can reach for when you want a put-together look that still feels comfortable. The goal is simple: a silhouette that reads polished, photographs well, and stays wearable for a full day or a long night.

Fit and sizing Fit is where most outfits win or lose. This design aims for a balanced shape with a defined line through the torso, a clean waist, and a smooth finish through the hips and legs. If you prefer a more relaxed feel, size up; if you like a closer fit, stay true to size. Sizes may include: One Size.

Fabric and comfort Comfort is not just about softness. It is also about movement and how the fabric behaves as you walk, sit, and stand. A fabric blend with a bit of give helps it keep its shape while still feeling wearable.

Highlights A clean neckline and a refined silhouette for an elevated look. Designed to layer easily with jackets, wraps, or sweaters. Works well with both minimal accessories and statement pieces.

How to style Styling ideas: keep it minimal with neutral shoes and one standout accessory. For a relaxed daytime look, add a denim jacket or cardigan. For events, switch to a bolder shoe and a small clutch for a sharper finish.

Color notes Available colors may include: Gray, White, Beige. If a shade is sold out, check back as availability can change.

Care Care guidance matters if you want it to keep its shape and finish. Follow the label first.
